message:
Good morning Cru! 

Heads up about this super cool event starting at SVC tonight! 

PRAYER MEETING STARTING TODAY
Three days of 24 hour prayer with Stadium Village Church will be starting today!! If you're interested, grab a few friends and sign up for 1 to 2 hour slots at the link below. There will be worship and a speaker from 7 to 9 PM Wednesday night, worship and prayer from 5-10pm Friday, and Saturday 7-9pm. There will also be evangelism training with pizza from 4 to 6 PM on Saturday if you wanted to join and then go on the streets that night.
Sign up here.
